com.xtructure.xneat.genetics
Class GeneMap

java.lang.Object
  com.xtructure.xneat.genetics.GeneMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<Gene>, java.util.Collection<Gene>
public class GeneMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Collection<Gene>

GeneMap is a collection of Genes that keeps track of several properties particular to the collection. It maintains:

  1. a mapping to genes from their ids.
  2. a mapping from node ids to the set of links incident on it (both incoming and outgoing)
  3. a mapping from node ids to the set of nodes connected to it (both incoming and outgoing)
as well as other simple statistics, such as link and node count.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
